{"id":340418,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/03/美国之音-广东茂名万人示威，反对px项目/","date":"2014-03-30T22:06:14Z","modified":"2014-04-02T13:30:50Z","title":"美国之音 | 广东茂名万人示威，反对PX项目","content":"<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/guangdong-maoming-protests/1882606.html\" name=\"ctl00_cpMain2_ctl00_ctl03_ctl00_repHeadlines_ctl02_ImageHyperlink1\"><img src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/92B3CA64-73B2-4ACE-801E-1BF06AD9D43B_w113_r1.jpg\"></a></div>\n<h4><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/guangdong-maoming-protests/1882606.html\">广东茂名万人示威，反对PX项目</a></h4>\n<div>广东省茂名市有数千市民游行示威，抗议政府建设PX（芳烃）项目；当局出动上千武警和特警，流传到网上的照片显示，一些市民被警察打伤。据目击者称，当地时间上午8点起，陆续有大量市民持“PX项目滚出茂名”等横幅、标语游行至茂名市政府，要求停建PX项目。示威一直持续到下午3点。 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/guangdong-maoming-protests/1882606.html\">更多</a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-linfeifan-20140330/1882550.html\" name=\"ctl00_cpMain2_ctl00_ctl03_ctl00_repHeadlines_ctl03_ImageHyperlink1\"><img src=\"http://www.voachinese.com/video/3e34104d-bf6f-494a-8dd1-04a8bfdeeb09.jpgx?w=113&amp;h=64\"></a></div>\n<h4><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-linfeifan-20140330/1882550.html\"><span><img border=\"0\" align=\"top\" src=\"http://www.voachinese.com/img/assignedIcons/icon-blank.gif\"> </span><span>海峡论谈:专访太阳花学运总指挥林飞帆 专家分析北京与美国立场</span></a></h4>\n<div>台湾太阳花学运创下抗议学生占领立法院13天，而且似乎要继续下去的纪录，并在星期天激出数十万黑衫军聚集在总统府前集会静坐，主导这场活动的核心灵魂人物&#8211;太阳花学运的总指挥林飞帆星期天接受美国之音海峡论谈节目专访。 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-linfeifan-20140330/1882550.html\">更多</a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/philippines-china-20140330/1882517.html\" name=\"ctl00_cpMain2_ctl00_ctl03_ctl00_repHeadlines_ctl04_ImageHyperlink1\"><img src=\"http://gdb.voanews.com/5DA27A6A-3A16-4745-93CE-A5E75B712F2D_w113_r1_cy6.jpg\"></a></div>\n<h4><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/philippines-china-20140330/1882517.html\">菲律宾指中国过度声索领土主权 向法庭提交证明</a></h4>\n<div>菲律宾星期天（3月30日）就其控告中国过度声称拥有南中国海领土主权一案，向海牙国际法庭提交了证明文件。 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/philippines-china-20140330/1882517.html\">更多</a></div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-multiple-city-relay-protest-20140330/1882501.html\" name=\"ctl00_cpMain2_ctl00_ctl03_ctl00_repHeadlines_ctl05_ImageHyperlink1\"><img src=\"http://www.voachinese.com/video/12191545-dd6d-4255-982f-6e842cb0cc4f.jpgx?w=113&amp;h=64\"></a></div>\n<h4><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-multiple-city-relay-protest-20140330/1882501.html\"><span><img border=\"0\" align=\"top\" src=\"http://www.voachinese.com/img/assignedIcons/icon-blank.gif\"> </span><span>海峡论谈: 多城市接力支持台湾学运</span></a></h4>\n<div>台湾太阳花学运扩大战线、遍地开花，3月30日除了有数十万黑衫军聚集在台湾总统府前集会静坐，海外留学生和台湾侨胞们也发起330全球跨时差接力串连活动，估计有17个国家、49个城市加入，从亚太的日本、澳大利亚，串连到欧洲各国以及美国东西岸各大城市。 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/r/http/www.voachinese.com/content/strait-talk-multiple-city-relay-protest-20140330/1882501.html\">更多</a></div>\n</div>\n<div><img src=\"http://fullrss.net/v/b5751a1dab57f57671c5d503ab58280b/http/www.voachinese.com/media/photogallery/maoming-guangdong-thousands-protest-px-projects/1882623.html\"></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://fullrss.net/\">fullrss.net</a></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n","a